this use, but let's stay focused here. So the flow

00:00:18.990 --> 00:00:22.570
for what you'll do in this question itself. Is first,

00:00:22.570 --> 00:00:25.535
you'll find a potential user. This could be a friend,

00:00:25.535 --> 00:00:29.180
co-worker, family member. Somebody who you think could

