here. Then you're actually going to do some very

00:00:34.590 --> 00:00:40.090
basic user-experience research. This will essentially be an interview

00:00:40.090 --> 00:00:42.640
with this person you know. We'll try and

00:00:42.640 --> 00:00:46.380
figure out the attributes about them as they pertain

00:00:46.380 --> 00:00:48.798
to the app you want to build. Now doing

