And we've provided a privy template which includes some suggested

00:00:54.570 --> 00:00:58.130
questions and categories of questions to think about. Once you've

00:00:58.130 --> 00:01:01.680
done your user research, you'll actually create a persona in

00:01:01.680 --> 00:01:04.730
this case, for the person you interviewed. Again, the template's

00:01:04.730 --> 00:01:07.530
going to be really helpful for this step. Some really key

00:01:07.530 --> 00:01:12.590
points when you're thinking about user research. First, be quiet.

00:01:12.590 --> 00:01:14.380
And by that, I mean the other person should be

00:01:14.380 --> 00:01:17.790
doing most of the talking. Try not to interrupt and

00:01:17.790 --> 00:01:21.980
definitely don't ever tell them they're wrong. Second, is to ask open questions.

00:01:23.000 --> 00:01:25.590
And by this, I mean, let's say you were to make a music app

00:01:25.590 --> 00:01:29.430
for this person. You shouldn't ask a question like: how much do you enjoy

00:01:29.430 --> 00:01:33.580
